      "text": [
        "476 - وَ كَانَ رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ إِذَا فَاتَتْهُ اَلصَّلاَةُ عَلَى اَلْمَيِّتِ صَلَّى عَلَى قَبْرِهِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.476 - \"The Messenger of Allah (sw), if he missed the funeral prayer for a deceased person, would offer the prayer at their grave”."
        ]
      }
    }
